Class AiccParser

java.lang.Object
dev.jcputney.elearning.parser.parsers.BaseParser<AiccMetadata,AiccManifest>
dev.jcputney.elearning.parser.parsers.AiccParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
ModuleParser
public class AiccParser extends BaseParser<AiccMetadata,AiccManifest>
Parses AICC (Aviation Industry CBT Committee) eLearning modules by reading INI-style files with specific extensions such as .crs, .des, .au, .cst, .ort, and .pre to extract core metadata and organize it in structured format.
